{
  "stem": "11722.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then they brought in, from the neighboring villages they brought in Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we lived in miserable conditions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] You could go out during the day, but there was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You had to be back by six o'clock.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my father fended for the family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We all did a part, and we all lived in real fear.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I remember listening to people, and they said it's 1944.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The Nazis are losing the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Maybe something is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Maybe they'll stop.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Everyone lived with hope.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We had to hope.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "That's part of life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And then word came that we were going to be resettled in the Hungarian prairie.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We would be put to work to help the war effort.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And to start preparing for evacuation, I remember my mother baking cookies, and we went through rehearsals, how many pair of pants we can put on, how we will take [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the necessary things along.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Everything was lured into-- you know, we-- I can't think of the word-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we went as far as preparing cooking utensils and beddings to take along.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I mean, their deception were such that to keep us calm, they did almost anything and everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I remember we didn't know when, but they said-- and I remember in May of 1944, we were awakened to gunshots and hollering and yelling.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And everybody out, and line up in the middle of the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they were whipping people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And I remember people [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] crying and praying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And they were cutting beards, and there was blood splattered all over.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
